<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c2">(٣٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{الرِّجْسَ مِنَ الْأَوْثَانِ}</span> ...<span class="c5"> القَذَارَةَ الَّتِي هِيَ:</span> الأَوْثَانُ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c2">(٣٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{قَوْلَ الزُّورِ}</span> ... الكَذِبَ وَالاِفْتِرَاءَ عَلَى اللهِ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(٣١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{حُنَفَاءَ لِلَّهِ}</span> ... مُسْتَقِيمِينَ عَلَى الإِخْلَاصِ مَائِلِينَ عَنِ الشِّرْكِ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(٣١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{سَحِيقٍ}</span> ... بَعِيدٍ مُهْلِكٍ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(٣٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{شَعَائِرَ اللَّهِ}</span> ... مَا أَشْعَرْتُمْ بِهِ، وَأَعْلَمْتُمْ؛ مِنْ أَعْمَالِ الحَجِّ وَالذَّبائِحِ الَّتِي تُنْحَرُ فِيهِ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(٣٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{لَكُمْ فِيهَا مَنَافِعُ}</span> ... يَحِلُّ الاِنْتِفَاعُ بِهَا بِالرُّكُوبِ، وَشُرْبِ اللَّبَنِ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(٣٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{مَحِلُّهَا}</span> ... وَقْتُ ذَبْحِهَا.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(٣٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{الْبَيْتِ الْعَتِيقِ}</span> ... الحَرَمِ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(٣٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{مَنسَكًا}</span> ... نُسُكًا وَعِبَادَةً؛ بِذَبْحِ الأَنْعَامِ تَقَرُّبًا لِلهِ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(٣٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{الْمُخْبِتِينَ}</span> ... الخَاضِعِينَ المُتَوَاضِعِينَ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c2">(٣٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَجِلَتْ}</span> ... خَافَتْ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c2">(٣٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَالْبُدْنَ}</span> ... الإِبِلَ، جَمْعُ بَدَنَةٍ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c2">(٣٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{شَعَائِرِ اللَّهِ}</span> ... أَعْلَامِ دِينِهِ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c2">(٣٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{صَوَافَّ}</span> ... قَائِمَاتٍ؛ قَدْ صُفَّتْ ثَلَاثٌ مِنْ قَوَائِمِهَا، وَقُيِّدَتِ الرَّابِعَةُ.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c2">(٣٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَجَبَتْ}</span> ... سَقَطَتْ عَلَى الأَرْضِ بَعْدَ النَّحْرِ.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span><span class="c2">(٣٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{الْقَانِعَ}</span> ... الفَقِيرَ الَّذِي لَمْ يَسْأَلْ تَعَفُّفًا.<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>